TGL_SCRIPTER - Key Generation System

This repository hosts the automatic, HWID-based key generation system for TGL_SCRIPTER projects. It ensures secure, device-specific access for all users while facilitating developer monetization.

Features

•
Automatic Key Generation: Keys are generated dynamically based on the user's unique HWID and the current date.

•
24-Hour Expiration: All keys automatically expire after 24 hours, ensuring consistent user engagement.

•
Zero Maintenance: The system requires no manual updates; the algorithm handles all key rotations.

•
Mobile Optimized: Designed for seamless performance on mobile executors like Delta and iOS.

How to Use

1.
Execute the TGL_SCRIPTER loader in your preferred executor.

2.
Click the "Get Key" button to copy your unique verification link.

3.
Complete the monetization steps to be redirected to this page.

4.
Copy your unique Daily Key and paste it into the loader to authenticate.

Developer Integration

To integrate this system into your own projects, ensure your Lua loader and the index.html file share the same SALT value. This "Secret Salt" is the foundation of the matching algorithm.




